      • addDeps

        public void addDeps(com.google.common.collect.ImmutableSet<Path> sourcePaths,
                    Iterable<BuildTarget> buildTargets,
                    DependencyType dependencyType)
        Record a dependency on a BuildTarget. The dependency's type will be merged if multiple TargetNodes refer to it or if multiple TargetNodes include sources from the same directory.
        Parameters:
        sourcePaths - the Paths to sources which need this dependency to build. Can be empty.
        buildTargets - the BuildTargets to depend on
        dependencyType - what is the dependency needed for.
